[29] DESCRIPTION -------------------------------------------------------------

Install and reload ~/.vimrc configurations in real-time.

[30] VERSION -----------------------------------------------------------------

0.0.0.2

[31] AUTHORS -----------------------------------------------------------------

Kostya Zolotarov <kostya.zolotarov@gmail.com>

[32] FEATURES ----------------------------------------------------------------

* Vim Bash configuration
* Vim C configuration

[33] EXAMPLES ----------------------------------------------------------------

Install Bash configuration and reload ~/.vimrc.

$ vimrc bash

Install C configuration and reload ~/.vimrc.

$ vimrc c

Display usage options and application version.

$ vimrc help

[34] INSTALL -----------------------------------------------------------------

Install the vimrc script to $(HOME) path.

$ make install

Uninstall the vimrc script to $(HOME) path.

$ make uninstall

